graph LR
    Notebooks[Notebooks<br/>Workbench Images]

    %% External Dependencies (Base Images and Libraries)
    Notebooks -->|base images| UBI9[UBI9 Python 3.9/3.11]
    Notebooks -->|IDE framework| JupyterLab[JupyterLab 4.2/3.6]
    Notebooks -->|pipeline authoring| Elyra[Elyra 3.x]
    Notebooks -->|ML framework| PyTorch[PyTorch 2.x]
    Notebooks -->|ML framework| TensorFlow[TensorFlow 2.x]
    Notebooks -->|GPU support| CUDA[NVIDIA CUDA 11.x/12.x]
    Notebooks -->|AMD GPU| ROCm[AMD ROCm 5.x/6.x]
    Notebooks -->|Intel XPU| IntelOneAPI[Intel oneAPI]
    Notebooks -->|IDE alternative| CodeServer[Code Server 4.x]
    Notebooks -->|R IDE| RStudio[RStudio Server 2024.04.2]
    Notebooks -->|CLI tools| OpenShiftCLI[OpenShift CLI oc]
    Notebooks -->|database clients| MongoDB[MongoDB CLI 6.0]
    Notebooks -->|database clients| MSSQL[MSSQL Tools 2022]

    %% Internal ODH Dependencies (Runtime)
    NotebookController[ODH Notebook Controller] -->|creates StatefulSet| Notebooks
    Dashboard[ODH Dashboard] -->|reads metadata| Notebooks
    Notebooks -->|API client| DSP[Data Science Pipelines]
    Notebooks -->|sidecar| OAuthProxy[OAuth Proxy]
    Notebooks -->|API client| ModelRegistry[Model Registry]
    Notebooks -->|API client| KServe[KServe Model Serving]
    Notebooks -->|storage| S3Storage[S3 Storage]

    %% External Services (Runtime)
    Notebooks -->|package install| PyPI[PyPI Registry]
    Notebooks -->|source control| Git[Git Repositories]
    Notebooks -->|data sources| ExternalDB[External Databases<br/>PostgreSQL/MySQL/MongoDB]
    Notebooks -->|cluster API| K8sAPI[Kubernetes API Server]
    Notebooks -->|authentication| OpenShiftOAuth[OpenShift OAuth]

    %% Build-time Dependencies
    Notebooks -.->|pulls images| ContainerRegistry[Container Registries<br/>Quay/Red Hat Registry]
    Notebooks -.->|CI/CD| Konflux[Konflux Pipeline]

    %% Integration Points
    DSP -.->|executes with| Notebooks
    NotebookController -.->|injects sidecar| OAuthProxy

